</li>
<li id="cite_note-9"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-9">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text"><cite id="CITEREFPrice2016" class="citation journal cs1">Price, Michael (2016). <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://doi.org/10.1126%2Fscience.aal0382">"European diseases left a genetic mark on Native Americans"</a>. <i>Science</i>. <a href="/wiki/Doi_(identifier)" class="mw-redirect" title="Doi (identifier)">doi</a>:<span class="id-lock-free" title="Freely accessible"><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://doi.org/10.1126%2Fscience.aal0382">10.1126/science.aal0382</a></span>.</cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.jtitle=Science&amp;rft.atitle=European+diseases+left+a+genetic+mark+on+Native+Americans&amp;rft.date=2016&amp;rft_id=info%3Adoi%2F10.1126%2Fscience.aal0382&amp;rft.aulast=Price&amp;rft.aufirst=Michael&amp;rft_id=https%3A%2F%2Fdoi.org%2F10.1126%252Fscience.aal0382&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AMassachusetts+smallpox+epidemic" class="Z3988"></span></span>
